Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:02.62,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I met Lain for the second time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.26,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,She looked straight at me and called me "Doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:10.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It made me so happy, that my face turned bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:13.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Maybe she's already figured me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.85,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If I get flustered just from being called "Doctor",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.96,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It's easy to tell that I'm pretty inexperienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:26.43,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But, I still get that weird feeling that I got when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.97,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I can't seem to place it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,When I look in her eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.10,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,it feels like she can see right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:41.31,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do I look unreliable to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:47.61,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Even so, I wish I was that calm when I was her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I wouldn't quite call her an elegant girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:59.56,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,but it's safe to say she seems pretty relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.01,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I thought she'd be acting like a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.57,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,but she really feels like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.65,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, they do say kids grow up pretty quick these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:14.82,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Lots of my relatives' kids are mature for their age too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Times are changing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.69,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ahhh, I'm starting to talk like an old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.94,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Don't let your hallucinations get to you, Lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.88,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll help you get better, I promise.
